column1: Mitch McConnell is one of the most evil people in America. He is vastly rich and laughs as his donors get rich and the American people get poorer. He hates poor people and pretends to care about Republican issues, but he only really cares about giving tax dollars to his donors. I hope Roy Moore gets elected and helps kick this senile old man out of power. The American people deserve better.
